      "fullTitleEng": "Napalkov State Budgetary Healthcare Institution «Saint-Petersburg clinical scientific and practical center for specialised types of medical care (oncological)",
      "shortTitle": "ГБУЗ «СПб КНпЦСВМП(о) имени Н.П. Напалкова»",
